  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>The Cat Farm Begins! 🐾🌴</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Live on the Island… and Survive!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a new life on a sunny island! Your cat has a small plot of land, but there’s a catch — rent is due every 5 days! Stay alive as long as you can by growing crops, completing orders, and enjoying the peaceful island life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Build, Upgrade, Expand! 🛠️</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and place useful structures to make your island more efficient!<br>Build garden beds, sprinklers, a grill, a well, a greenhouse, a humidifier, and more. Design your perfect workflow and keep your farm running smoothly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/dcde8f3fe9371e0bc76415654ba0ed4d.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/dcde8f3fe9371e0bc76415654ba0ed4d.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Plant It. Care for It. Harvest It! 🌱</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy seeds, plant crops, water them daily, and harvest fresh produce. Sell what you grow or use it to cook meals — all to earn coins and pay rent on time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/35086d5b5c9212f6c446c07c375728fc.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/35086d5b5c9212f6c446c07c375728fc.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Fire Up the Grill! 🍢</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The grill is your kitchen companion! Use fresh vegetables to prepare delicious dishes and fulfill customer orders. Cooking is a vital part of survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/06c59fea9fe30a188982992781fd3c89.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/06c59fea9fe30a188982992781fd3c89.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Cast a Line and Relax 🎣</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break and go fishing! Catch fish, complete fishing-related tasks, and unlock new opportunities as you enjoy life by the sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/33d3e62465a915993190d70becfe5d3d.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/33d3e62465a915993190d70becfe5d3d.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Decorate Your Island 🌺</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add your personal touch! Lay down paths, plant flower beds, and place decorations to make your island a cozy, stylish home in the middle of the ocean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Customize Your Cat 🐱</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cat, your style! Choose glasses, backpacks, hats, and fur color to create a look that’s all your own. Show off your feline farmer in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/2e47a5d44573bb276ac7231fe80fe2e0.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/2e47a5d44573bb276ac7231fe80fe2e0.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Time Flies… Rent Is Coming</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The days pass quickly on the island. Every 5 days, rent is due. Plan ahead, manage your resources, and don’t let your island dream fade away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready for the challenge?</strong><br><br><i><strong>Meowland: Island Farm</strong></i><strong> is waiting for you! 🐾</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>The Cat Farm Begins! 🐾🌴</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Live on the Island… and Survive!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a new life on a sunny island! Your cat has a small plot of land, but there’s a catch — rent is due every 5 days! Stay alive as long as you can by growing crops, completing orders, and enjoying the peaceful island life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Build, Upgrade, Expand! 🛠️</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and place useful structures to make your island more efficient!<br>Build garden beds, sprinklers, a grill, a well, a greenhouse, a humidifier, and more. Design your perfect workflow and keep your farm running smoothly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/dcde8f3fe9371e0bc76415654ba0ed4d.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/dcde8f3fe9371e0bc76415654ba0ed4d.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Plant It. Care for It. Harvest It! 🌱</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy seeds, plant crops, water them daily, and harvest fresh produce. Sell what you grow or use it to cook meals — all to earn coins and pay rent on time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/35086d5b5c9212f6c446c07c375728fc.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/35086d5b5c9212f6c446c07c375728fc.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Fire Up the Grill! 🍢</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The grill is your kitchen companion! Use fresh vegetables to prepare delicious dishes and fulfill customer orders. Cooking is a vital part of survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/06c59fea9fe30a188982992781fd3c89.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/06c59fea9fe30a188982992781fd3c89.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Cast a Line and Relax 🎣</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break and go fishing! Catch fish, complete fishing-related tasks, and unlock new opportunities as you enjoy life by the sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/33d3e62465a915993190d70becfe5d3d.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/33d3e62465a915993190d70becfe5d3d.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Decorate Your Island 🌺</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add your personal touch! Lay down paths, plant flower beds, and place decorations to make your island a cozy, stylish home in the middle of the ocean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Customize Your Cat 🐱</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cat, your style! Choose glasses, backpacks, hats, and fur color to create a look that’s all your own. Show off your feline farmer in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/2e47a5d44573bb276ac7231fe80fe2e0.poster.avif?t=1745765499\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369340/extras/2e47a5d44573bb276ac7231fe80fe2e0.webm?t=1745765499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Time Flies… Rent Is Coming</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The days pass quickly on the island. Every 5 days, rent is due. Plan ahead, manage your resources, and don’t let your island dream fade away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready for the challenge?</strong><br><br><i><strong>Meowland: Island Farm</strong></i><strong> is waiting for you! 🐾</strong></p>",
